{
  "texts": [
    "Subsequently, to further investigate SVs absent from the Manta call sets, we additionally genotyped the respective Sniffles2 calls against the raw Illumina read alignments for the same brain region (cingulate cortex) as well as a different brain region (cingulate white matter) using svtyper (version 0.7.1) 61.",
    "SVs reported as having at least one supporting read by svtyper were considered as present in a sample.",
    "PCR validation of selected mosaic deletions.",
    "We used the National Center for Biotechnology Information (NCBI) primer design tool to obtain primers straddling the target deletions.",
    "The primer sequences for the 240-bp deletion were TACCAAGTCTTTCTCCAAGTCCC (forward) and TTGCACAGCCTTGGCTATACTC (reverse) and, for the 127-bp deletion, ATCCTGAGAGAACCCCCTCC (forward) and GGACA-GACTCGTGGTTTCGT (reverse)."
  ]
}